title: Billy Mitchell Got Away With It... For Now…
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a long running lawsuit between infamous gamer Billy Mitchell and Twin Galaxies settling and why it might not be as much of a victory as Billy thinks. Thanks for watching!
